{"article_id":"9w4Q068TxXFaIHSJ","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The directed killing of Gen. Qassem Soleimani , Iran 's blood-soaked field marshal in the `` forever war '' of the Mideast , has begun to roil the politics of both the region and the U.S .","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"A stunned and shaken Iran retaliated","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"by firing a dozen missiles at two U.S. bases in Iraq .","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"Yet ,","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"before launching the attack ,","depth":11},{"id":5,"text":"Iran signaled","depth":11},{"id":6,"text":"that its retaliation would be strictly proportionate ,","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"to avoid an escalation .","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"U.S. forces were warned","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"where the missiles would hit .","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"Result :","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"zero U.S. casualties in the two strikes .","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"Hours after the Iranian missiles hit the U.S. bases , however ,","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"an apparently panicked Iranian officer at an air defense missile battery launched and shot down a Ukrainian airliner","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"leaving Tehran airport with 176 people aboard .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"For days , the ayatollah indicated","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"he did not know","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"the cause of the disaster had been one of Iran 's own surface-to-air missiles .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"Thus ,","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"while hundreds of thousands had been marching last week in nationalist solidarity","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"to honor the dead general ,","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"today , thousands of Iranians are marching against the ayatollah ,","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"accusing his regime of having known the truth","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"and lied to the nation .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"In Iraq , a nonbinding vote has been taken in parliament","depth":5},{"id":25,"text":"to demand a full U.S. military withdrawal from Iraq for the execution of Soleimani .","depth":5},{"id":26,"text":"President Donald Trump is threatening the Iraqis with sanctions","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"if Baghdad follows through","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"and expels the 5,200 U.S. troops still there .","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"NATO allies with units in Iraq are silently seething ,","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"as they received no warning","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"we were about to take down the general .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"Here , the political fallout from the execution of Soleimani has only just begun .","depth":4},{"id":33,"text":"Democrats ,","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"after denouncing Soleimani as a war criminal and serial killer of American soldiers ,","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"are accusing Trump of carrying out ,","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"without the consent of Congress ,","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"a premeditated act of war on a nation","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"on which Congress has n't authorized war .","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"Trump 's claim","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"that the general had to be taken down","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"to abort an `` imminent '' attack on Americans ,","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"including attacks on not one but four U.S. embassies ,","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"is being derided .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"The justice","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"of killing the general","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"seems less the issue now than the wisdom of the act ,","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"and a storm is brewing","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"over whether Trump and his aides have been dissembling .","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"Speaker Nancy Pelosi has already pushed through the House a nonbinding resolution","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"asserting","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"that Trump has no authority","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"to carry out acts of war against Iran","depth":14},{"id":53,"text":"without Congress ' consent .","depth":14},{"id":54,"text":"Rep. Matt Gaetz , a Trump supporter from Florida , stunned the president","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"by voting for the Pelosi resolution .","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"Sen. Mike Lee , R-Utah , broke with Trump","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"to denounce the briefing","depth":13},{"id":58,"text":"that Congress received ,","depth":13},{"id":59,"text":"about attacks on Americans being imminent ,","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"as both contemptuous and the worst briefing","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"he ever had .","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"The general may have gotten the justice","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"he deserved","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"in that SUV","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"departing Baghdad airport ,","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"but the unintended consequences of his execution are now coming in .","depth":6},{"id":67,"text":"Trump has elevated the Mideast wars as a major issue in 2020 , not his strong suit .","depth":5},{"id":68,"text":"For ,","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"as the military says ,","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"`` The enemy gets a vote ! ''","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"as to how much blood ,","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"including American blood ,","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"will be shed in 2020 .","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"Also ,","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"by sending the 82nd Airborne to Kuwait and Iraq ,","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"Trump underscored the truth :","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"We are still mired in the `` endless wars '' of the Mideast","depth":6},{"id":78,"text":"despite his promise","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"to extricate us .","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"Fractures have appeared in the conservative-populist coalition","depth":5},{"id":81,"text":"that put Trump in office .","depth":5},{"id":82,"text":"War Party interventionists ,","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"who have long sought to have the United States do to Iran what Bush 43 did to Iraq ,","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"are exhilarated by what","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"they believe","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"the Soleimani killing portends","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"-an inevitable war with Iran .","depth":6},{"id":88,"text":"Trump has also energized the anti-war majority in the Democratic Party , specifically the candidacy of Bernie Sanders ,","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"whose anti-war and anti-interventionist credentials are as long-standing and solid","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"as is his fidelity to socialism .","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"Sanders voted against both the Bush II Iraq War","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"that Sen. Joe Biden voted to support ,","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"and George H.W . Bush 's Desert Storm expulsion of the Iraqi army from Kuwait .","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"With the killing of the general and the possibility of a U.S.-Iran war rising ,","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"Bernie is the Democratic candidate","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"whose anti-war credentials are the longest and strongest","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"and whose position","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"of avoiding war with Iran","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"is most in sync with the majority of the party","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"he seeks to lead .","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"Sanders could ride anti-war sentiment to victory in Iowa and New Hampshire","depth":6},{"id":102,"text":"and have the wind behind him","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"going into South Carolina and Super Tuesday .","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"His socialism may be a bridge too far for most Americans , and an insuperable obstacle to his ever becoming president ,","depth":6},{"id":105,"text":"but","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"should he win the nomination ,","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"he could occupy in 2020 the space","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"Trump occupied in 2016 , as the anti-interventionist , anti-war candidate .","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"And","depth":6},{"id":110,"text":"if Bernie ran a `` Come Home , America '' campaign ,","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"half a century after the slogan 's author , George McGovern , lost in history 's largest landslide ,","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"Sanders could change the face and future of American politics .","depth":7},{"id":113,"text":"Patrick Buchanan has been an adviser to three presidents , a two-time candidate for the Republican presidential nomination , and the nominee for the Reform Party in 2000 .","depth":5},{"id":114,"text":"He was also a founding member of `` The McLaughlin Group , ''","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"which began on NBC ,","depth":7},{"id":116,"text":"and CNN 's `` Capital Gang '' and `` Crossfire . ''","depth":6},{"id":117,"text":"His latest book is :","depth":5},{"id":118,"text":"`` The Greatest Comeback :","depth":6},{"id":119,"text":"How Richard Nixon Rose From Defeat","depth":7},{"id":120,"text":"to Create the New Majority . ''","depth":7},{"id":121,"text":"For more of his reports , Go Here Now .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":243,"left":201,"right":242,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":201,"left":153,"right":200,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":153,"left":145,"right":152,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":145,"left":139,"right":144,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":139,"left":133,"right":138,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":133,"left":0,"right":132,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":123,"right":131,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":127,"right":130,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":127,"left":125,"right":126,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":125,"left":3,"right":124,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":124,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":126,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"le